{"id":20598,"date":"2021-12-15T16:41:27","date_gmt":"2021-12-15T15:41:27","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/?p=20598"},"modified":"2022-01-19T11:24:14","modified_gmt":"2022-01-19T10:24:14","slug":"golden-heights-issues-senior-secured-bonds","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/en\/assignment\/golden-heights-issues-senior-secured-bonds\/","title":{"rendered":"Golden Heights issues senior secured bonds"},"content":{"rendered":"<p class=\"preamble\">Skandinaviska Enskilda Banken (publ) (\u201dSEB\u201d) has acted as arranger and issuing agent in connection with Golden Heights AB (publ) (\u201cGolden Heights\u201d) issue of senior secured bonds in an initial amount of SEK 340\u00a0millions within a framework amount of SEK 600\u00a0millions. The proceeds from the issue of bonds will partially be used to refinance existing bonds. Golden Heights intends to list the bonds on Nasdaq Stockholm, Corporate Bond List.<\/p>\n<p>Golden Heights is the leading jewellery retailer in Sweden, and one of the leading actors in Finland, with well-known brands such as Guldfynd, Hallbergs Guld, Albrekts Guld, Lyxxa and Kultajousi.<\/p>\n<p>SEB was advised by Mannheimer Swartling in the transaction.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Skandinaviska Enskilda Banken (publ) (\u201dSEB\u201d) has acted as arranger and issuing agent in connection with Golden Heights AB (publ) (\u201cGolden Heights\u201d) issue of senior secured\u2026<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":10,"featured_media":20325,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[4313],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-20598","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-assignment","business-group-banking-and-finance"],"acf":[],"lang":"en","translations":{"en":20598,"sv":20596},"pll_sync_post":[],"_links":